ParallelChunk.en:
Fishing is the perfect example of global activity due to the globalisation of the resource, namely the fish, which have no regard for national borders; 
          therefore
         international laws are the only appropriate response.

From south to north, every area has its peculiarities; 
          however
        , the Convention which we adopt for ratification by the Member States provides cover in every instance and for fishermen's every need.
